<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id78921fce-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1960—<ref href="/us/pl/86/624">Pub. L. 86–624</ref> substituted “State” for “Territorial”.</p>
</note>
